libiges
------------------------------------------
Implementation of the IGESv5.3 specification

Runtime requirements:
  cygwin-3.6.7-1
  libgcc1-13.4.0-1
  libiges-devel-0.3+git20210523-1bl1
  libiges0-0.3+git20210523-1bl1
  libintl8-0.22.5-1
  libsisl4-4.6.0-1bl2
  libstdc++6-13.4.0-1
  pkg-config-2.5.1-1

Build requirements:
(besides corresponding -devel packages)
  binutils-2.46-1
  cmake-4.2.1-1
  cygport-0.37.7-1
  gcc-core-13.4.0-1
  gcc-g++-13.4.0-1
  libsisl-devel-4.6.0-1bl2
  ninja-1.13.2-1

Canonical website:
  https://github.com/cbernardo/libIGES

Canonical download:
  https://github.com/cbernardo/libIGES.git

-------------------------------------------

Build instructions:
  1. unpack libiges-0.3+git20210523-X-src.tar.xz
  2. if you use setup to install this src package,
     it will be unpacked under /usr/src automatically
        % cd /usr/src
        % cygport ./libiges-0.3+git20210523-X.cygport all

This will create:
  /usr/src/libiges-0.3+git20210523-X-src.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libiges-0.3+git20210523-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libiges0-0.3+git20210523-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libiges-devel-0.3+git20210523-X.tar.xz

-------------------------------------------

